('Bam BiÃ¨re', 395, 5, 74, 4.500000, 'An artisan farmhouse ale that is golden, naturally cloudy, bottle conditioned and dry hopped for a perfectly refreshing balance of spicy malts, hops and yeast.', 'Jolly Pumpkin Artisan Ales', 'United States'),
