('Misfit Red', 4489, 3, 33, 5.100000, 'This medium bodied amber ale has a smooth, malt character with a hint of roasted (dark) malt flavor. This beer has just enough hops to balance and goes well with many foods.', 'DuClaw', 'United States'),
