('Damnation', 4498, 5, 72, 7.000000, 'Damnation has extraordinary aromas of banana and pear with mouth filling flavors of sweet malt and earthy hops. The lingering finish is dry and slightly bitter but very, very smooth.', 'Russian River Brewing', 'United States'),
