('NÃ¸gne Ã˜ Bitter', 5051, 1, 3, 4.500000, 'A light session ale, with an assertive hop aroma of E K Golding.  Great beer to pair with lots of different food - a good allround.', 'NÃ¸gne Ã˜ - Det KompromisslÃ¸se Bryggeri A/S', 'Norway'),
