('LeRoy\'s Brown Ale', 5098, 3, 38, 5.300000, 'Brewed in honor of Andrewâ€™s Grandfather LeRoy, this big bad nut brown ale has a fantastic malt character made up of caramel and chocolate flavors. One taste and you will see why this is the baddest beer in the whole damn town!!!', 'Rivertowne Pour House', 'United States'),
('Melting Pot Pale Ale', 5099, 3, 26, 5.500000, 'If you liked the Nobleman this one should blow you away! We took malt and hops from around the world to create this International Pale ale! This beer has an incredible amount of hop flavor and the perfect hop bite!', 'Rivertowne Pour House', 'United States'),
