('Frosted Frog Christmas Ale', 5780, 11, 141, 8.600000, 'The essence of Christmas is captured in this very bottle you are holding. Perfectly blended spices compliment Frosted Frogâ€™s rich malt flavors, creating the ultimate Christmas experience. Celebrate the holidays as you savor this very special seasonal offering.', 'Hoppin Frog Brewery', 'United States'),
('Fresh Frog Raw Hop Imperial Pale Ale', 5781, 3, 26, 7.800000, 'Special hoppy flavors and aromas are captured by adding freshly picked, undired hops during the harvest.\n\n\nThese wet hops impart a character unlike other brews, that is quite unique and satisfying for those who love hops â€“ the spice of beer. Smell the hop fields, smell the freshness.', 'Hoppin Frog Brewery', 'United States'),
('Frog\'s Hollow Double Pumpkin Ale', 5782, 11, 123, 8.400000, 'There\'s a Place just south they call Frog\'s Hollow, with cauldrons afire in Fall, and they only speak in whispers of the name. There\'s a brewery they say who has the secret, of spices picked just right. With a crying shout, they\'ll knock it out, and hand you this Frog\'s delight.', 'Hoppin Frog Brewery', 'United States'),
('Outta Kilter Wee-Heavy Scotch Red Ale', 5783, 1, 15, 8.200000, 'Rich, malty flavors of caramelized and toasted grains dominate this strong Scotch ale. A hint of rye adds a crisp, Scotch-like, old-world beer character, reminiscent of a simpler life from centuries ago. â€œIt is a wee bit heavyâ€', 'Hoppin Frog Brewery', 'United States'),
