('One Oatmeal Stout', 5801, 1, 21, 0.000000, 'Number one in a series of five stouts produced to help ease you through the cold and grey midwestern winters. This beer is full bodied with hints of chocolate, roasted barley, coffee flavors and a nice creamy head.', 'Dark Horse Brewing Co.', 'United States'),
