('Duet', 5804, 3, 31, 7.000000, 'A West Coast IPA. Our original single IPA made with Simcoe and Amarillo hops â€œin harmony.â€ 1.065 OG 45 IBU 7%ABV', 'Alpine Beer Company', 'United States'),
