('Kryptonite Imperial IPA', 5825, 3, 32, 9.000000, 'American style double IPA, full bodied malt flavor supports a ridiculous amount of hops, giving it pronounced bitterness and overwhelming hop flavor and aroma. Made with 5 pounds of hops per barrel.', 'Iron Hill Brewery - Wilmingon', 'United States'),
