('IPA Series (Zeus)', 5830, 3, 31, 0.000000, 'A series of single hop, small batch IPAs brewed in Camp Hill. These IPAs showcase the bitterness, flavor, and aroma of each particular hop variety.', 'Appalachian Brewing Company', 'United States'),
