('Abita Amber', 5903, 7, 82, 0.000000, 'Abita Amber is a Munich style lager. It has a smooth, malty, slightly caramel flavor and a rich amber color.', 'Abita Brewing Company', 'United States'),
('S.O.S', 5904, 7, 77, 0.000000, 'Save Our Shores (S.O.S) is an unfiltered weizen pils and has a brilliant golden color. A Charitable Pilsner', 'Abita Brewing Company', 'United States'),
('Abita Golden', 5905, 8, 95, 0.000000, 'Abita Golden is a crisp, clean continental lager. Just four ingredients are all it takes.', 'Abita Brewing Company', 'United States'),
('Abita Light Beer', 5906, 8, 96, 0.000000, 'Uniquely hand-crafted using 100% all natural ingredients: The result is the smoothest, most flavorful light beer.', 'Abita Brewing Company', 'United States'),
('Abbey Ale', 5907, 1, 1, 0.000000, 'Abbey Ale is a strong malty ale brewed in the style of the Trappist Monks. 22oz bottles only', 'Abita Brewing Company', 'United States'),
('Wheat', 5908, 7, 82, 0.000000, 'Abita Wheat is a lager, not ale, and contains a generous amount of wheat which produces a clean, simple flavor.', 'Abita Brewing Company', 'United States'),
('Triple Citra Hopped Satsuma Wit', 5909, 11, 121, 0.000000, 'Similar to the Harvest Wit but with a lot more punch. A very pronounce citrus aroma with a triple hop flavor makes for one great beer.', 'Abita Brewing Company', 'United States'),
('Honey Rye Ale', 5910, 11, 128, 0.000000, 'This beer is not very bitter which allows the flavors of the rye and honey to come through. The result is a full bodied, sweet, and malty beer.', 'Abita Brewing Company', 'United States'),
('Strawberry', 5911, 11, 121, 0.000000, 'Strawberry Harvest Lager is a wheat beer made with real Louisiana strawberries.', 'Abita Brewing Company', 'United States'),
('Satsuma Wit', 5912, 11, 121, 0.000000, 'This Wit beer has a sweet and subtle citrus flavor with a touch of spice that is cool and refreshing.', 'Abita Brewing Company', 'United States'),
('Abhi beer', 5913, 7, 89, 0.000000, '', 'Abhi Brewery', 'India'),
('Ambr', 5914, 11, 132, 0.000000, '', 'Brasserie du Bouffay', 'France');
